      "name": "Full-load design point hemolysis validation (5 L/min, 3500 RPM)",
      "description": "CFD hemolysis index compared against bench measurements at nominal VAD operating point. Monte Carlo UQ with 10 000 samples propagates inlet velocity, viscosity, and RBC fragility uncertainty. Predicted HI = 0.0041 ± 0.0008 (95% CI); measured HI = 0.0044 ± 0.0006. Validation metric E = 6.8%, within MRL-5 acceptance band of 15%.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/monte-carlo-fullload-10k"
