      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed: coarse (4.2M cells), medium (11.8M cells), fine (28.6M cells). GCI on fine mesh = 3.8% for hemolysis index at design point. Time-step refinement study completed. Spatial error on secondary QoIs (wall shear stress distribution) not fully characterized; achieved level 3."
    },
