      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles measured via PIV with ±2.1% uncertainty. Hematocrit maintained at 40% ± 1.5%. Temperature controlled at 37°C ± 0.5°C. Pump casing geometry tolerances not fully documented for all test articles; achieved level 3 versus required 4."
    },
    {
