      "rationale": "Validation metric computed for 4 of 5 operating points with full combined uncertainty bands. Partial-load point (3 L/min, 3000 RPM) comparison uses point-estimate prediction only; aleatory uncertainty in RBC fragility assessed qualitatively rather than through a structured UQ propagation, leaving the combined uncertainty band incomplete for that condition. Achieved level 3 versus required level 5."
    },
